title: (1) Elation Dmx Branch X4 Dmx Booster/Splitter
item_description:
(1) Elation Dmx Branch X4 Dmx Booster/Splitter

(1) Elation Dmx Branch X4 Dmx Booster/Splitter

DMX-BRANCH/4™ is a DMX signal splitter/booster that splits a single DMX signal into four separate outputs, as well as boosts the signal for extended cable runs usually associated with large permanent installations. DMX-BRANCH/4™ includes a set of 3pin and 5pin DMX inputs, a set of 3pin and 5pin DMX outputs for linking up to 4 additional units, 4 sets of 3pin and 5pin isolated DMX outputs, a link out/terminate switch, and DMX data LED indicators for each of the four DMX outputs. Flexible installation options are possible like truss mounting using the included 3/16” (4.7625mm) threaded hole for a clamp (not included), and a 19-inch rack mounting kit is included.

Photos are representative of this item.
